&lt;p&gt;The main idea of Antrecote&amp;amp;Co: local products, new approaches to smoked meat and fish and a supremacy of taste.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Menu comprises a wide assortment of stakes &ndash; from ribeye to porterhouse. Special attention is paid to fish &ndash; dishes are cooked using complicated technics to achieve delicate taste and aroma.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;In the restaurant there is a small shop where you can buy fresh or cooked meat, fish and seafood.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Antrecote&amp;amp;Co is located in the trade center &ldquo;Sphera&rdquo;, just under the glass cupola. Interior is designed in classic style with use of natural materials &ndash; wood, glass and natural fabrics. There is a summer veranda with panoramic view to modern Moscow.&lt;/p&gt;
